```{r setup, include=FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = TRUE)
library(lubridate)
library(tidyverse)
```

```{r}
df <- read.csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alondra170/stat-4355-project/main/Top500.csv")
summary(df)
df$added <- ymd(df$added)
df$dur <- as.numeric(df$dur)
df <- df[!duplicated(df), ]
summary(df)
dfnumerics <- df %>% select(year, bpm, nrgy, dnce, dB, live, val, dur, acous, spch, pop)
lm <- lm(data = dfnumerics, pop ~ .)
summary(lm)
hist(dfnumerics[1:11])
```
